==Notes==
*{{note label|Mens500|a|a}} No bronze medal was awarded in this event because two competitors tied for second place with a time of 40.5 seconds.<ref name="SSMen's500" />
*{{note label|Mens1500|b|b}} No bronze medal was awarded in this event because two competitors tied for second place with a time of 2 minutes 5.0 seconds.<ref name="SSMen's1500" />
*{{note label|Womens500|c|c}} No bronze medal was awarded in this event because three competitors tied for second place with a time of 46.3 seconds.<ref name="SSWomen's500" />

